）全球0800【全球疫情汇总】据新浪实时统计，截至3月12日8点，除中国（包括港澳台地区）以外，海外新冠肺炎累计确诊44738例，死亡1446例，治愈5079例。
According to Sina Real-Time Statistics, as of 8: 00 on March 12, there were 44,738 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia abroad, 1,446 deaths and 5,079 cures, excluding China (including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan).
注：新增0表示当天暂未宣布数据。
Note: A new zero indicates that data were not announced for that date.
数据来源：新浪0800【世卫组织说新冠肺炎疫情可称为大流行】世界卫生组织总干事谭德塞说，新冠肺炎疫情从特征上可称为大流行。
Source: Sina 0800 [WHO says the outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia could be called a pandemic] World Health Organization Director General Lindsay Tan said the outbreak could be characterized as a pandemic.
他强调，新冠肺炎传播可被遏制，呼吁各国加强防疫措施。
He stressed that the spread of pneumonia could be contained, and called on countries to strengthen epidemic prevention measures.
世卫组织上一次宣布“大流行”是在2009年的“猪流感（H1N1）”期间。
The last time the WHO declared a pandemic was during the swine flu (H1N1) in 2009.
0800【世卫组织：中国以外新冠肺炎确诊病例达37371例】世卫组织每日疫情报告显示，截至欧洲中部时间11日10时（北京时间11日17时），中国以外新冠肺炎确诊病例较前一日增加4596例，达到37371例；中国以外死亡病例较前一日增加258例，达到1130例。
0800 [WHO: 37371 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia outside China] As of 10: 00 (11: 00 Beijing time) Central Europe time, the number of confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia outside China had increased by 4,596 to 37,371 compared with the previous day.
0800【世贸组织员工确诊感染新冠肺炎，世贸组织暂停会议】美国0800【确诊病例已达1281例，24州及华盛顿特区宣布进入紧急状态】美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学发布的实时统计数据显示，截至美国东部时间11日19时13分，美国累计新冠肺炎确诊病例已达1281例。
0800 Confirmation of New Crown Pneumonia by WTO Staff Suspended Meeting 1 800 confirmed cases have been declared a state of emergency in 24 states and Washington D.C. Real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University show that as of 19: 13 a.m. EDT, the cumulative number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in the United States had reached 1,281.
据美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）报道，24个州和华盛顿特区已宣布进入紧急状态。
Twenty-four states and Washington, D.C., have declared a state of emergency, CNN reported.
0800【特朗普签署备忘录：加强医护人员口罩保障】0800【哥伦比亚广播公司2名员工的新冠病毒检测呈阳性】公司已经确认了可能与这些人有过直接接触的员工。
0800 [Trump Sign Memorandum: Enhance Medical Mask Protection] Two CBS employees who tested positive for the new crown virus have identified employees with whom they may have had direct contact.
他们将被要求自我隔离并远程工作14天。
They will be asked to isolate themselves and work remotely for 14 days.
0800【华盛顿州、旧金山等多地发布禁令禁止大型集会活动】意大利0800【意大利关闭全国除食品店和药店外的所有商铺】意大利总理孔特在电视讲话中说，公共交通、物流、邮局、银行和食品生产行业将正常营业和运转，以保证对公众的基本生活服务。
Italy closes all shops except food stores and pharmacies Italian Prime Minister Matteo Conte said in a televised address that public transport, logistics, post offices, banking and food production would operate normally to guarantee basic services to the public.
孔特表示，希望两周后能看到这些严控措施产生的效果。
Mr Conte said he hoped to see the effects of these controls in two weeks.
0800【尤文图斯后卫鲁加尼确诊】意甲俱乐部尤文图斯官方宣布，队中后卫鲁加尼的新冠肺炎病毒检测结果呈阳性，目前没有症状。
Juventus defender Roberto Rogani has confirmed that his defender has tested positive for the new crown pneumonia virus and is asymptomatic.
尤文图斯阵中拥有包括C罗、迪巴拉、基耶利尼等在内的多位世界级球星。
Juventus have a number of world-class stars, including Ronaldinho, Debala and Gielini.
