0800 [2313 new confirmed cases of crown pneumonia, 12,462 cumulative new cases of death 196, cumulative 827 deaths.
西班牙0800【新冠肺炎确诊病例破两千，单日新增506例】截至当地时间11日13时，西班牙累计确诊病例达2128例，其中47人死亡，142人病情危重，183人治愈出院。
Spain 0800 [New Crown Pneumonia confirmed cases more than 2,000 cases, a one-day increase of 506 cases By 1300 local time, Spain has a cumulative total of 2,128 confirmed cases, of which 47 died, 142 were in critical condition and 183 were cured.
目前，西班牙确诊病例有近一半集中于马德里大区，累计达1024例，死亡病例中也有31例位于该地区。
At present, nearly half of the confirmed cases in Spain are concentrated in the Madrid region, with a cumulative total of 1,024, and 31 of the deaths are in the region.
法国0800【新冠肺炎确诊病例增至2281例，死亡病例48例】法国总统马克龙将于当地时间12日晚8时发表全国电视讲话，讲话内容与目前的公共卫生危机有关。
French President Nicolas Sarkozy will deliver a national television address about the current public health crisis at 8: 00 pm local time, raising the number of confirmed cases to 2,281 and 48 deaths.
德国0800【默克尔警告六七成德国人将感染新冠病毒】这意味着，德国8200万民众中可能有多达5700万人染病。
German Chancellor Angela Merkel has warned that 60-70% of Germans could get the new crown virus, meaning as many as 57 million of Germany's 82 million people could be infected.
截至11日，德国新冠肺炎确诊病例已超过1500例，死亡3人。
More than 1,500 cases and three deaths have been confirmed in Germany as of November 11.
据德国病毒学专家德罗斯滕此前预测，德国可能有27.8万人死于新冠肺炎。
German virologist Drogsten had previously predicted that 278,000 people could die from pneumonia in Germany.
英国0800【新冠肺炎确诊病例增至456例，累计死亡6例】丹麦0800【新增252例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计514例】丹麦首相弗雷泽里克森宣布，非履行关键职能的政府公务人员将从3月13日回家休假，时间长达两周；所有学校和幼儿园将从3月16日起关闭两周；禁止所有超过100人的活动，而不是此前要求的1000人；所有室内文化机构（包括图书馆与各大休闲设施）从3月13日起关闭两周；所有教育机构的学生从3月13日起停课两周。
Britain's 0800 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia have risen to 456 cases, with a cumulative total of 514 new cases of DNK 0800. Danish Prime Minister Fraziriksen announced that government officials not performing key functions would be closed for two weeks from March 13, all schools and kindergartens from March 16, all indoor cultural institutions (including libraries and major leisure facilities) for two weeks.
瑞典0800【新增145例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计500例】首都斯德哥尔摩累计233例，死亡1例。
Sweden 0800 [145 new cases of new crown pneumonia confirmed, cumulative total of 500 cases in the capital Stockholm 233 cases, one case of death.
奥地利0800【累计246例新冠肺炎确诊病例，学校即将全面停课】芬兰0800【新增25例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计65例】希腊0800【首现新冠肺炎死亡病例】死者为一名男性退休教授，曾于2月27日结束赴以色列和埃及的旅行回到希腊。
AUSTRIA 0800 [Accumulated 246 Cases of New Crown Pneumonia, School Closed Soon] Finnish 0800 [New Crown Pneumonia Confirmed Cases, 65 Cases Cumulatively] The deceased, a retired male professor, returned to Greece on February 27 after a trip to Israel and Egypt.
