Australia 0800 Confirmed Cases of New Crown Pneumonia Up to 128 Cases in Iran Cumulatively 9000 Cases Accumulated New Crown Virus Infected by First Vice President Jahangiri Qatar 0800 [New Crown Pneumonia confirmed by First Vice President Jahangiri] total of 262 cases.
确诊病例中22例死亡，包括国内感染的15人，以及“钻石公主”号邮轮的乘客7人。
Twenty-two of the confirmed cases were fatal, including 15 internal infections, and seven passengers on board the MV Princess Diamond.
