2007-09-25 21: 40 (Israel 0800 Confirmed New Crown Pneumonia) The death toll from Albania's 0800 case is 73-year-old woman who traveled to Bologna, Italy.
埃及0800【新冠肺炎确诊病例增至67例】韩国0800【首都圈暴发99人聚集性感染，专家担心出现第三波疫情高峰】这是疫情发生以来韩国首都圈发生的最严重聚集性感染事件。
Egypt 0800 New Crown Pneumonia Confirmed 67 Cases South Korea's 0800 outbreak of 99 people in the capital, experts fear a third wave of the epidemic's peak, the worst case of concentrated infection in the South Korean capital since the outbreak.
印度0834【印度孟买首次报告新冠肺炎确诊病例】印度金融中心孟买11日晚确诊2例新冠肺炎病例。
India's first confirmed cases of pneumonia reported in Mumbai, India The Indian financial center, Mumbai, confirmed 2 cases of new crown pneumonia on the night of Tuesday.
孟买所在的马哈拉施特拉邦卫生部门通报说，两名新冠肺炎确诊患者与此前在孟买附近城市浦那被确诊的一对印度夫妇为同一迪拜旅行团成员。
Mumbai's Maharashtra state health ministry reported that two newly diagnosed cases of pneumonia and a previously diagnosed Indian couple in Pune, near Mumbai, are members of the same Dubai tour group.
0800【确诊病例升至68例，将全面禁止外国游客入境】印度政府决定从13日起暂时取消所有外国游客的访印签证。
The Indian government has decided to suspend all foreign tourists from visiting India as of September 13.
